## 👥 About Us

> **We, Team JundAlNabi, are a group of Black Hat Hackers.**

We are a dedicated team of BlackHat Hacker enthusiasts united by a common drive — breaking barriers, and pushing the limits of technology.

---

## 🔥 Who We Are

| Role | Description |
|------|-------------|
| 🔴 Red Team | Offensive security & penetration testing |
| 💻 Exploit Dev | Binary Exploitation & Pwn |
| 🕵️ OSINT | Open Source Intelligence gathering |
| 🔍 Reverse Eng | Malware analysis & reverse engineering |

---

## ⚙️ Our Skills

```
✔ Web Application Exploitation
✔ Reverse Engineering
✔ Binary Exploitation (Pwn)
✔ Cryptography
✔ Forensics & OSINT
✔ Network Security
✔ Malware Analysis
```

